data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER offering $5,000 in concessions!!!  This practically new (built in 2020) craftsman style 2 level home sitting on 2 acres has 5 bedrooms, 4 full baths, a beautiful formal dining area with a coffered ceiling, and an office. The kitchen has beautiful white cabinets and a large island overlooking the large living room with a fireplace. There's also a fireplace on the back porch when you're looking to relax outdoors and enjoy the big fenced in backyard. The huge owner's suite has trey ceilings, a beautiful newly built-in mantel and newly installed luxury vinyl flooring. There's new custom lighting throughout the home and the home has been freshly painted. There's also a second bedroom with a full bath attached. This home has all the space you could need and comes with a refrigerator, washer and dryer (all purchased in 2023). It also comes with 2 televisions that are already mounted.   While you will have the serenity of living in Cataula, the fun is not far away.  A short 20 minute drive and you will find ample entertainment, shopping, eateries and more in Columbus, GA.  You'll also be a short drive to the beautiful Callaway Gardens in Pine Mountain, GA.  Need to travel? The Columbus Airport is also about 20 miles away.    Come take a look!
